name: Hit Et Nunc - Full Circle Gltich
description: Made to celebrate 10 years of art on the blockchain and 10,000 artworks - the beginning of a new exciting period with Hit Et Nunc as our saviour! The emergence of Hit En Nunc has come at the perfect time. Just as Cryptoart was about to descend into fame, fortune and meaningless art - along comes hit En Nunc, bringing us full circle - back to the grass roots ethics of the early days of punk, glitch art and cryptoart. 10k divided by 10 = 1000 - enough for us all x
